                            <li>Keep a charged phone with you at all times</li>
                            <li>Avoid displaying expensive items or large amounts of cash</li>
                            <li>Use reputable transportation services</li>
                            <li>Stay in well-lit, populated areas at night</li>
                            <li>Inform someone of your daily plans</li>
                            <li>Learn basic local emergency phrases</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Property Safety -->
                <div class="tip-card during animate-on-scroll">
                    <div class="tip-header">
                        <span class="tip-icon">🔍</span>
                        <span class="tip-category">Property Check</span>
                        <h3 class="tip-title">Safety Inspection</h3>
                    </div>
