                <p class="section-subtitle">Use these interactive checklists to ensure you've covered all safety aspects of your stay.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="checklist-grid">
                <div class="checklist-card animate-on-scroll">
                    <h3 class="checklist-title">Arrival Checklist</h3>
